data.description: This spacious home features an abundance of natural light, a cozy fireplace, vaulted ceilings, and striking beamed ceilings. The thoughtfully designed layout  creates a warm and inviting atmosphere, making this delightful residence a perfect choice for those seeking a comfortable and enjoyable living experience. With four bedrooms and three and a half bathrooms, this home offers both comfort and functionality.  This beautiful property features a lush lawn and a detached storage building, perfect for storing all your outdoor items. Located near everything the area has to offer, this property provides a great location for those who want to be close to all the amenities. Situated on a large lot, the property offers plenty of space for outdoor activities and entertainment.  Call your agent today for a showing. To help visualize this home’s floorplan and to highlight its potential, virtual furnishings may have been added to photos found in this listing
